display_long_description:
Car Parking Realistic Driving Simulator is a fully immersive VR car parking game for Meta, crafted for fans of driving simulators, parking games, and driving school experiences.

Step into the driver’s seat and tackle 100+ handcrafted levels, divided into Easy, Medium, and Hard modes. Each level is built around realistic layouts with tight spaces and precise turns, designed to improve your parking accuracy and control.

In Arcade Mode, test your reflexes and speed in an open parking zone. Parking spots change dynamically, and you must park your car repeatedly within a limited time (e.g., 6 minutes) to earn a high score.

 This isn’t just about steering — your virtual car 🚗 is fully equipped:

👉  A car sensor shows proximity to nearby obstacles
👉   A TV display gives a live rearview from the back camera
👉   Functional left and right side mirrors
👉   Gear shifting between Drive (D) and Reverse (R) for realistic control

🏆 Key Features:

✅    Immersive VR controls & realistic car physics
✅    First-person driver view with full dashboard functionality
✅    Dynamic Arcade Mode and 100+ structured levels
✅    Ideal for fans of realistic car games and parking challenges

Step into the driver’s seat — in full  VR. Master tight turns, conquer obstacle-filled parking lots, and feel every bump as if you’re really there. Can you prove you’re the ultimate VR parking master?

Ready to master every maneuver and become a VR parking pro?  Add to Wishlist — New Cars & Tracks Coming Soon!
